snippet: After narrow losses to No. 13 Michigan and No. 10 Ohio State, Northwestern kept its hopes alive for its first trip to the N.C.A.A. tournament with a victory at Iowa.

headline.main: Victory Over Iowa Keeps Northwestern Hoping
